# Copy to .env.local for local dev, and set these as Build environment
# variables in Cloudflare Pages (they are inlined at build time).
# Both are public values (they ship in the client bundle) — that is expected.

# Web3Forms access key — powers the quote/contact form.
# Get a free key at https://web3forms.com using sales@gawhrat.com.
# If unset, the form falls back to a pre-filled WhatsApp message.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=

# Google Analytics 4 Measurement ID (looks like G-XXXXXXXXXX).
# From your GA4 property → Admin → Data Streams. If unset, analytics is off.
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=
